sql_query.sql:
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT 1 AS one FROM "categories" WHERE ((FALSE AND LENGTH(COALESCE(email_in, '')) > 0 AND email_in_allow_strangers)
          OR categories.id NOT IN (SELECT category_id FROM category_groups)
          OR categories.id IN (
                SELECT category_id
                  FROM category_groups
                 WHERE permission_type IN (1)
                   AND (group_id = 0 OR group_id IN (SELECT group_id FROM group_users WHERE user_id = 1410))
             )) LIMIT 1) subquery_for_count
